FBIS4-30549 "dreas124_c_94034" FBIS-EAS-94-124 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 North Korea WPK Secretary Meets Outgoing Indian Ambassador WPK Secretary Meets Outgoing Indian Ambassador SK2806105894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1030 GMT 28 Jun 94 SK2806105894 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 28 (KCNA) -- The secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea, Hwang Chang-yop, met and conversed with the outgoing Indian Ambassador to Korea, Shehkholen Kipgen, when the latter paid a farewell call on him today.
